{"tid":854090,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"(校園 愛情 少少真人真事) 《追尋真愛》","createTime":"2018-10-09T06:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T07:32:18.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a797a139f37c7af0c09c1aa5b2a2fb0078d4f5c","tid":854090,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"Hello<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次個籃球故唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爛左尾<br />\n今次我決定試多一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得呢D題材，應該容易寫得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我遲少少先出故，始終我多野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499ed06927aa09158446a4997ab27f1bc0f0a7b5","tid":854090,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"序<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇聽過自閉症？<br />\n<br />\n應該好多人都聽過，但你未必知道患者的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n其實，係好痛苦的。<br />\n<br />\n「收皮啦！你呢D弱智仔，一世都冇可能有女！」呢句，係我初中果陣，係學校聽得最多的說話。<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為，自閉＝弱智，其實唔係。<br />\n<br />\n自閉的人，只要有人幫助，都可以打開自己的心靈，與其他人共處。<br />\n<br />\n我，就係其中一個。"},{"pid":"6ad2f3ab20e4ab63d36434da11fe5dacd38f7411","tid":854090,"uid":182110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"Lm"}]}